text.tspan: GDP per head vs share of services in GDP, 1800 to 2016
The vertical axis shows historical estimates of the share of services in GDP (estimated at current prices). The horizontal axis shows GDP per
head after adjusting for inflation and price differences across countries (figures are in 2011 international-$).
Data source: OWID based on Herrendorf et al. (2014) and GGDC-10 (2015); Maddison Project Database 2020 (Bolt and van Zanden, 2020)
